import { Route, Routes } from "react-router-dom"
import { Home } from "./home"
import { Login } from "./login"
import { Menu } from "./menu"
import { Personall } from "./personall"
import { Showimg } from "./showimg"


export const Routing = () => {
      return <Routes>
            <Route path="home_pg" element={<Home></Home>}>
                  <Route path="myimg/:myparameter" element={<Showimg></Showimg>}></Route>

            </Route>
            <Route path="login_pg" element={<Login></Login>}></Route>
            <Route path="menu_pg" element={<Menu></Menu>}></Route>
            <Route path="personall_pg" element={<Personall></Personall>}></Route>




      </Routes>





}
